name: Static_minusTest
description: Unit tests for the Static.minus method, which removes an element from a list.

test_cases.name: testMinus_ElementPresent
test_cases.description: Tests the Static.minus method when the element to be removed is present in the list.

test_cases.name: testMinus_ElementNotPresent
test_cases.description: Tests the Static.minus method when the element to be removed is not present in the list.

test_cases.name: testMinus_EmptyList
test_cases.description: Tests the Static.minus method when the input list is empty.
